                        Enter "SMECH ?" for template

                               Some examples
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
                            Show ARC-2R Archer:
                                SMECH ARC-2R

                    Show all CLAN WarHammer variations:
                               SMECH whm CLAN
                            SMECH warhammer CLAN

                            Show all 75 tonners:
                                 SMECH T 75

                        Show all mechs in database:
                                   SMECH
                                SMECH SHORT


                               Flag Meanings:
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
                      Q .................. Quad design
                      E ................... Endo-Steel
                      X .................... XL Engine
                      M ......................... MASC
                      F ................ Ferro-Fibrous
                      D ............ Double Heat Sinks
                      C ......................... CASE


